Home.title: Hello, I`m a
Home.description: Be an enthusiastic, dynamic, responsible person at work. Constantly learning to cultivate old and new knowledge about programming to develop more professional skills. With the current knowledge, there are many shortcomings, I want to find a suitable workplace and stick with it for a long time along with adding the missing knowledge. My goal in the next two years is to become a full-stack programmer.

about.head: About Me
about.heading: I`m a Nguyen Anh Viet and
about.description: Be an enthusiastic, dynamic, responsible person at work. Constantly learning to cultivate old and new knowledge about programming to develop more professional skills. With the current knowledge, there are many shortcomings, I want to find a suitable workplace and stick with it for a long time along with adding the missing knowledge. My goal in the next two years is to become a full-stack programmer.
